---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Data Policy">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-gray-800">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Spatchat.org Data Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-10">Last Updated: 05/2025</p>

    <div class="space-y-10">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Data Collection & Use</h2>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mt-4">User-Uploaded Data</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-base">
          <li>GeoTIFFs, CSVs, or other spatial data uploaded for analysis are:
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li>Processed ephemerally (deleted after 7 days unless retained by user request).</li>
              <li>Never used for training AI models without explicit opt-in.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mt-4">Cookies & Analytics</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-base">
          <li>We use anonymized Google Analytics to improve UX (no personal identifiers).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Data Sharing & Ownership</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-base">
          <li>Your data is private by default and never shared.</li>
          <li>You may opt-in to contribute anonymized datasets to:
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li>Public benchmarking (hosted on <a href="https://datadryad.org" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Dryad</a>).</li>
              <li>Open-source model improvement (via <a href="https://huggingface.co" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Hugging Face</a>).</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Code & AI Models</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-base">
          <li><strong>All code:</strong> <a href="https://github.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">GitHub</a> (MIT License)</li>
          <li><strong>AI models:</strong> <a href="https://huggingface.co" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Hugging Face</a> (Apache 2.0)</li>
          <li><strong>Archives:</strong> Major releases archived via <a href="https://zenodo.org" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Zenodo</a> (DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.XXXX)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Security</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-base">
          <li>Encryption in transit (HTTPS) and at rest (AES-256).</li>
          <li><strong>Note:</strong> Do not upload PII (e.g., field coordinates of endangered species).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Compliance</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 text-base">
          <li>Aligned with NSF data management requirements.</li>
          <li>Compliant with <abbr title="Findable, Accessible, Interoperable, Reusable" class="underline decoration-dotted cursor-help">FAIR</abbr> principles.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">6. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-base">
          Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:spatchat.org@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">spatchat.org@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
